2canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fneet-ug-2024-paper-leak-case-cbi-arrests-mastermind-2-mbbs-students-who-acted-as-solvers%2Farticleshow%2F111888802.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Organic%20Farming%20Scheme%20Wilts%20In%20Soil%20Of%20Corruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%2016.37%20lakh%20hectares%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20the%20largest%20area%20under%20organic%20farming%20in%20the%20country%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20give%20this%20a%20boost%20has%20fallen%20prey%20to%20corruption%2C%20an%20investigation%20has%20revealed.%20Crores%20of%20rupees%20earmarked%20to%20promote%20the%20environmentally%20friendly%20method%20of%20farming%2C%20which%20is%20good%20for%20the%20soil%2C%20crops%20and%20even%20consumers%2C%20have%20allegedly%20been%20swindled%20by%20local%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20said%20it%20will%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20take%20appropriate%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Anuppur%20district%2C%20the%20local%20administration%20conducted%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20and%20found%20that%20the%20money%20allocated%20from%20the%20District%20Mineral%20Fund%20in%202019-20%20to%20promote%20organic%20farming%20in%20the%20area%20has%20been%20misappropriated.%20The%20administration%20has%20now%20recommended%20that%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20and%20the%20Agriculture%20Department%20take%20action%20against%20the%20officials%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20plan%2C%205%2C000%20farmers%20from%20various%20villages%20in%20the%20district%20were%20to%20receive%20vermicomposting%20beds%2C%20organic%20manure%2C%20earthworms%2C%20nets%2C%20literature%2C%20and%20training.%20Accordingly%2C%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%206.93%20crore%20was%20allocated%20from%20the%20fund%2C%20out%20of%20which%20Rs%202.9%20crore%20was%20allocated%20to%20the%20Agriculture%20Department's%20Agricultural%20Technology%20Management%20Agency%20(ATMA)%20Project%2C%20Anuppur%2C%20to%20procure%20materials%2C%20Rs%202.93%20lakh%20for%20training%20and%20other%20works%2C%20and%20Rs%201.08%20crore%20was%20given%20to%20a%20private%20company%20for%20soil%20testing.%20The%20allotment%20per%20farmer%20was%20Rs%209%2C770.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%20Missing%2C%20Training%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20NDTV%20visited%20villages%20like%20Baskhali%20and%20Changeri%20in%20Kotma%20block%20and%20spoke%20to%20farmers%20who%20were%20supposed%20to%20have%20benefited%20from%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20findings%20were%20alarming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F26620fio_madhya-pradesh-organic-farming-story_625x300_20_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Baskhali%2C%20the%20vermicompost%20beds%20provided%20to%20farmers%2C%20which%20are%20made%20of%20material%20akin%20to%20tarpaulin%2C%20were%20found%20to%20be%20spread%20out%20over%20roofs%20to%20protect%20houses%20from%20the%20rain.%20Farmer%20Motilal%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20net%20and%20a%20bed%20for%20vermicomposting%2C%20but%20no%20earthworms.%20Without%20them%2C%20the%20other%20materials%20were%20useless%2C%20and%20no%20compost%20was%20ever%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ffp5uj3g8_madhya-pradesh-organic-farming-story_625x300_20_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Singh%2C%20another%20farmer%2C%20had%20to%20purchase%20earthworms%20himself%20to%20make%20compost.%20Four%20other%20farmers%2C%20Kamlesh%2C%20Sunita%2C%20Lalman%2C%20and%20Hiralal%2C%20also%20echoed%20the%20complaints%20and%20added%20that%20they%20never%20received%20the%20soil%20testing%20reports%20which%20would%20enable%20them%20to%20understand%20how%20much%20compost%20to%20use%20or%20what%20crops%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Changeri%2C%20farmer%20Belan%20Singh%20Marko%20stated%20that%20no%20training%20was%20provided%2C%20and%20the%20nets%20and%20beds%20were%20left%20unused%20in%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5hft8qjg_madhya-pradesh-organic-farming-story_625x300_20_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20villages%20like%20Gohindra%2C%20Pathraudi%20Manmari%2C%20and%20Perichua%20too%2C%20farmers%20reported%20receiving%20incomplete%20materials%20and%20no%20training.%20Former%20district%20panchayat%20member%20Buddhsen%20Rathore%20said%20he%20was%20the%20first%20to%20raise%20these%20issues%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Will%20Act'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttempts%20to%20contact%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20Anuppur%20Agriculture%20Department%20and%20the%20ATMA%20project%20director%20were%20unsuccessful.%20The%20investigation%20and%20complaint%20letters%20have%2C%20however%2C%20reached%20the%20Agriculture%20Department%20and%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Aidal%20Singh%20Kansana%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWherever%20there%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20corruption%2C%20we%20investigate%20and%20take%20action.%20I%20will%20talk%20to%20the%20collector%20of%20Anuppur.%20If%20any%20such%20thing%20is%20found%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action%20against%20the%20guilty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721482620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fbj43ndmo_madhya-p