0Cup%2C%20now%20finds%20himself%20in%20an%20interesting%20spot.%20A%20Hindustan%20Times%20report%20has%20said%20that%20Pandya's%20place%20in%20the%20ODIs%20is%20also%20not%20guaranteed.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fgambhir-reminded-hardik-call-details-of-selection-meeting-casts-doubt-over-pandyas-odi-future-101721379368254.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20a%20BCCI%20official%20as%20saying%20that%20Gambhir%20called%20Pandya%20and%20told%20him%20to%20play%20the%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20to%20prove%20his%20bowling%20fitness.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHardik%20was%20also%20reminded%20by%20Gambhir%20on%20the%20call%2C%20that%20he%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20see%20him%20bowl%20his%20full%20quota%20in%20ODIs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20a%20BCCI%20official%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20news%20agency%20IANS%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Kaif%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F247-mohammad-kaif-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Kaif%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Hardik%C2%A0Pandya%C2%A0'shayad%20captain%20banne%20chahiye%20the'%20(for%20Sri%20Lanka%20tour).%20Hardik%20has%20captained%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans%20for%20two%20years%20and%20in%20their%20first%20year%20itself%2C%20they%20made%20it%20to%20the%20final...Hardik%20has%20experience%20captaining%20the%20T20I%20side.%20He%20was%20also%20the%20vice-captain%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20coach%20has%20arrived%2C%20there%20will%20be%20new%20planning.%20Surya%20is%20also%20a%20good%20player%2C%20he%20has%20been%20playing%20for%20years.%20He%20is%20a%20No.1%20T20%20player%2C%20I%20hope%20he%20will%20shoulder%20the%20captain's%20responsibility%20well.%20But%20I%20feel%20they%20should%20have%20backed%20Hardik%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGambhir%20is%20an%20experienced%20captain%20and%20coach...He%20understands%20cricket%20very%20well.%20I%20think%20'Hardik%20ne%20aisa%20koi%20galat%20kaam%20nhi%20kia%20ki%20unko%20captaincy%20na%20mile'%20(Hardik%20has%20not%20done%20anything%20wrong%20that%20he%20should%20not%20get%20the%20captaincy).%20He%20has%20experience%2C%20has%20captained%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20leading%20a%20new%20team%20(Gujarat%20Titans)%20to%20the%20trophy%2C%20with%20fresh%20and%20young%20faces%2C%20which%20is%20a%20huge%20thing.%20He%20has%20made%20the%20Titans%20win%20by%20working%20from%20Ground%20Zero%20in%20the%20IPL...I%20think%20he%20was%20entitled%20to%20the%20captaincy.%20So%20let's%20just%20wait%20and%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721481480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3infotn8_hardik-pandya_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-reminded-by-gautam-gambhir-report-reveals-india-coachs-stern-message-over-odi-future-6141530%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20India's%20vice-captain%20at%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20now%20finds%20himself%20in%20an%20interesting%20spot%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-reminded-by-gautam-gambhir-report-reveals-india-coachs-stern-message-over-odi-future-6141530%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-reminded-by-gautam-gambhir-report-reveals-india-coachs-stern-message-over-odi-future-6141530%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-reminded-by-gautam-gambhir-report-reveals-india-coachs-stern-message-over-odi-future-6141530%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manolo%20Marquez%20Appointed%20Head%20Coach%20Of%20Indian%20Men's%20Football%20Team%3A%20AIFF%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20(AIFF)%20on%20Saturday%20announced%20the%20appointment%20of%20Spaniard%20Manolo%20Marquez%20as%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20men's%20football%20team.%20Marquez%20is%20currently%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20Indian%20Super%20League%20(ISL)%20side%20FC%20Goa.%20Commenting%20on%20the%20development%2C%20AIFF%20president%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20delighted%20to%20welcome%20Mr.%20Marquez%20to%20this%20important%20role%20and%20are%20also%20thankful%20to%20FC%20Goa%20for%20their%20generosity%20of%20releasing%20him%20for%20national%20duty.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20Mr.%20Marquez%20in%20the%20years%20ahead.%20The%20AIFF%2C%20FC%20Goa%2C%20and%20Mr.%20Marquez%20will%20collaborate%20closely%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20minimal%20impact%20between%20the%20two%20jobs%20and%20strive%20to%20achieve%20the%20best%20possible%20results%20for%20all%20involved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%202024-25%20season%2C%20Mr.%20Marquez%20will%20continue%20his%20role%20as%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20first%20team%20at%20FC%20Goa%2C%20handling%20both%20responsibilities%20concurrently%20before%20assuming%20the%20national%20coaching%20role%20on%20a%20full-time%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AIFF%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20appointment%20Marquez%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20honour%20for%20me%20to%20be%20the%20National%20Football%20Team%20coach%20of%20India%2C%20a%20country%20I%20consider%20my%20second%20home.%20India%20and%20its%20people%20are%20something%20I%20feel%20attached%20to%20and%20I%20feel%20a%20part%20of%20since%20I%20first%20came%20to%20this%20beautiful%20country.%20I%20want%20to%20do%20my%20best%20to%20bring%20success%20to%20the%20millions%20of%20fans%20we%20have.%20I%20am%20very%20grateful%20to%20FC%20Goa%20for%20allowing%20us%20the%20flexibility%20to%20help%20the%20national%20team%20during%20the%20coming%20season%20while%20I%20am%20still%20the%20club's%20head%20coach.%20I'm%20grateful%20to%20the%20AIFF%20for%20this%20opportunity%20and%20we%20hope%20to%20do%20great%20things%20for%20football.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAged%2055%2C%20Manolo%20Marquez%20has%20extensive%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20of%20Indian%20football%20and%20coaching%20national%20team%20players%2C%20especially%20youngsters.%20Many%20national%20team%20players%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20were%20called%20up%20from%20his%20Hyderabad%20FC%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarquez%20has%20been%20coaching%20in%20India%20since%202020.%20He%20has%20coached%20two%20ISL%20clubs%20-%20his%20first%20stint%20was%20with%20Hyderabad%20FC%20(2020-23)%2C%20before%20he%20switched%20over%20to%20FC%20Goa%20(2023-present).%20He%20is%20an%20ISL%20Cup%20winner%20with%20Hyderabad%20FC%20in%202021-22.%20Overall%2C%20Marquez%20had%20an%20extensive%20coaching%20career%20in%20Spain%20-%20Las%20Palmas%20(top%20division)%20and%20Las%20Palmas%20B%2C%20Espanyol%20B%2C%20Badalona%2C%20Prat%2C%20Europa%20(third%20division).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721480520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fiokns5u_manolo_650x400_20_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fmanolo-marquez-appointed-head-coach-of-indian-mens-football-team-aiff-6148553%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aged%2055%2C%20Manolo%20Marquez%20has%20extensive%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20of%20Indian%20football%20and%20coaching%20national%20team%20players%2C%20especially%20youngsters%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fmanolo-marquez-appointed-head-coach-of-indian-mens-football-team-aiff-6148553%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fmanolo-marquez-appointed-head-coach-of-indian-mens-football-team-aiff-6148553%2Famp%2F1%