d-head-coach-of-indian-mens-football-team%2Farticleshow%2F111887656.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chirag%20Paswan%20pitches%20for%20pan-India%20caste%20census%2C%20but%20with%20a%20condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721480088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111887382%2Cimgsize-702828.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchirag-paswan-pitches-for-pan-india-caste-census-but-with-a-condition%2Farticleshow%2F111885887.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20a%20key%20ally%20of%20the%20NDA%20in%20Bihar%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census%2C%20arguing%20it%20helps%20the%20government%20develop%20schemes%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bupliftment%20of%20castes.%26quot%3B%20Paswan%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20LJP%20(Ram%20Vilas)%2C%20opposes%20making%20the%20census%20data%20public%2C%20fearing%20it%20could%20cause%20%26quot%3Bdivision%20in%20society.%26quot%3B%20Paswan%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20caste%20census%20for%20government%20planning%20but%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20societal%20impacts%20if%20the%20data%20were%20disclosed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchirag-paswan-pitches-for-pan-india-caste-census-but-with-a-condition%2Farticleshow%2F111885887.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Retest%2C%20Haryana%20NEET%20Centre%20With%20Most%20Top%20Scorers%20Gave%20This%20Result...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20NEET%20testing%20centre%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20had%20six%20students%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks%2C%20now%20shows%20a%20stark%20contrast%20with%20no%20one%20scoring%20above%20682%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20city-wise%20results%20declared%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20the%20NEET%20results%20revealed%20that%20Hardayal%20Public%20School%20in%20Haryana's%20Bahadurgarh%20had%20a%20total%20of%20494%20students%20appearing%20for%20the%20exam.%20Among%20them%2C%20the%20highest%20score%20was%20682%2C%20achieved%20by%20only%20one%20student.%20Additionally%2C%20only%2013%20students%20managed%20to%20score%20above%20600%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20centre%20began%20when%20the%20NEET%20exam%20data%20was%20uploaded%20earlier%2C%20showing%20six%20students%20with%20perfect%20scores.%20%C2%A0Additionally%2C%20two%20candidates%20scored%20718%20and%20719%20marks%20respectively.%20The%20improbability%20of%20such%20a%20feat%20led%20to%20widespread%20suspicion%20and%20uproar.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20intervened%2C%20cancelling%20the%20grace%20marks%20that%20had%20been%20awarded%20and%20ordering%201%2C563%20candidates%20to%20retake%20the%20exam.%20Of%20these%2C%20about%20800%20students%20appeared%20for%20the%20re-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20announced%20the%20centre%20and%20city-wise%20results%20following%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%20The%20results%2C%20initially%20declared%20on%20June%205%2C%20were%20re-published%20to%20mask%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20aspirants.%20This%20measure%20aimed%20to%20determine%20whether%20candidates%20from%20allegedly%20tainted%20centres%20scored%20disproportionately%20high%20marks%20compared%20to%20those%20from%20other%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20exam%2C%20held%20on%20May%205%2C%20took%20place%20across%204%2C750%20centres%20in%20571%20cities%2C%20including%2014%20international%20locations%2C%20accommodating%20over%2024%20lakh%20candidates.%20Allegations%20of%20irregularities%2C%20including%20a%20paper%20leak%2C%20have%20put%20the%20exam%20under%20intense%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20resume%20hearings%20on%20the%20matter%20on%20July%2022%2C%20addressing%20multiple%20petitions%20seeking%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20exam%2C%20a%20re-test%2C%20and%20a%20court-monitored%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20malpractice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV's%20Analysis%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV's%20analysis%20of%20the%20NEET%20data%20also%20spotlighted%20two%20other%20centres%20-%20Oasis%20Public%20School%20in%20Bihar's%20Hazaribagh%2C%20and%20Jalaram%20International%20in%20Gujarat's%20Godhra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Oasis%20Public%20School%2C%20where%20the%20principal%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20paper%20leak%20case%2C%20701%20students%20took%20the%20exam.%20The%20highest%20score%20here%20was%20below%20700%2C%20with%20seven%20students%20scoring%20above%20650%2C%2023%20above%20600%2C%20and%2046%20above%20550.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalaram%20International%20School%20reported%20that%201%2C838%20students%20appeared%20for%20NEET.%20The%20highest%20score%20was%20under%20700%2C%20with%20five%20students%20scoring%20above%20650%2C%2014%20above%20600%2C%20and%2031%20above%20550.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20suggest%20that%20these%20scores%20are%20within%20expected%20ranges%20and%20do%20not%20indicate%20anomalies.%20However%2C%20contrasting%20results%20from%20an%20Ahmedabad%20centre%2C%20where%2012%20of%20676%20students%20scored%20above%20700%2C%20may%20raise%20questions%20during%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20India%2C%20the%20town%20of%20Sikar%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20notable%20hub%20for%20NEET%20success%2C%20with%20students%20from%20this%20district%20achieving%20record-breaking%20marks.%20Remarkably%2C%20149%20students%20from%20Sikar%20have%20scored%20over%20700%20marks%2C%20setting%20a%20high%20benchmark%20in%20the%20national%20examination.%20In%20addition%2C%202%2C037%20students%20from%20the%20area%20have%20secured%20more%20than%20650%20marks%2C%20and%20a%20total%20of%204%2C297%20students%20have%20achieved%20scores%20above%20600.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-nine%20of%20the%2050%20top-performing%20centres%20are%20located%20in%20Sikar.%20A%20total%20of%206%2C038%20students%20from%20Sikar%20attained%20more%20than%20550%20marks%2C%20and%208%2C225%20students%20surpassed%20the%20500-mark%20threshold.%20This%20exceptional%20success%20has%20taken%20both%20teachers%20and%20parents%20by%20surprise%2C%20as%20such%20a%20high%20concentration%20of%20top%20scores%20from%20a%20single%20district%20is%20unprecedented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajkot%20School%20of%20Engineering%20in%20Gujarat%20stands%20out%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20top%20scorers.%20Out%20of%201%2C968%20students%20who%20appeared%20at%20this%20centre%2C%20112%20achieved%20scores%20above%20700-the%20highest%20among%20all%20centres.%20Additionally%2C%20112%20students%20scored%20above%20650%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPowai%20Engineering%20College%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Numakkal%20saw%201%2C017%20students%20sit%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20with%20only%20two%20students%20surpassing%20700%20marks%20and%2052%20students%20achieving%20over%20650%20marks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721479560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm6tes5mg_neet-protest_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-results-neet-ug-after-retest-haryana-neet-centre-with-most-top-scorers-gave-this-result-6147854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20NEET%20testing%20centre%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20had%20six%20students%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks%2C%20now%20shows%20a%20stark%20contrast%20with%20no%20one%20scoring%20above%20682%20in%20the%20city-wise%20results%20of%20declared%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-results-neet-ug-after-retest-haryan