22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'When%20Biharis%20Are%20Doing%20So%20Well%2C%20Why%20Is%20Bihar%20Behind%2C'%20Asks%20Union%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20leader%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20asked%20the%20Bihar%20government%20to%20set%20a%20precedent%20by%20taking%20stringent%20action%20in%20cases%20of%20crime%20and%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20bridge%20collapses%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20state%20needs%20a%20vision%20to%20move%20up%20the%20development%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20sharp%20critic%20of%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20JD(U)%20president%20Nitish%20Kumar%20before%20both%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20said%20the%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20will%20fight%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections%20under%20Mr%20Kumar's%20leadership%20but%20flagged%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20which%2C%20he%20suggested%2C%20has%20stymied%20the%20state's%20growth.The%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Bihar%20are%20due%20to%20be%20held%20around%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBihari%20itna%20aage%20hai%20to%20Bihar%20itna%20peeche%20kyon%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(When%20Biharis%20are%20doing%20so%20well%2C%20then%20why%20is%20Bihar%20so%20behind%3F)%20We%20need%20to%20find%20an%20answer%20to%20this%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Paswan%20told%20PTI%2C%20highlighting%20how%20people%20from%20the%20state%20in%20different%20fields%2C%20from%20elite%20government%20jobs%20to%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20have%20done%20well%20after%20migrating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20that%20a%20vision%20needs%20to%20be%20there%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20efforts%20should%20be%20made%20to%20stop%20migration%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Union%20budget%20presentation%20on%20July%2023%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20said%20he%20supported%20the%20demand%20for%20special%20category%20status%20for%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20the%20NITI%20Aayog's%20recommendations%20go%20against%20granting%20the%20demand%20and%20said%20an%20alternative%20like%20a%20special%20package%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20collapse%20of%20nearly%2015%20bridges%20in%20Bihar%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20a%20development%20which%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20development%20work%20and%20made%20the%20state%20a%20magnet%20for%20jokes%20and%20memes%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20said%20it%20is%20a%20serious%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20definitely%20shows%20that%20somewhere%20corruption%20has%20taken%20place.%20Compromises%20were%20made.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20into%20the%20politics%20of%20who%20was%20in%20the%20government%20then.%20We%20are%20in%20the%20government%20now.%20It%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20make%20sure%20this%20does%20not%20get%20repeated.%20Whosoever%20is%20responsible%20should%20be%20held%20accountable%20and%20punished%20so%20that%20a%20precedent%20is%20set%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20change%20of%20stand%20on%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20he%20said%20if%20he%20is%20part%20of%20an%20alliance%2C%20then%20he%20needs%20to%20be%20there%20wholeheartedly.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20be%20part%20of%20an%20alliance%20and%20have%20apprehensions%20also.%20Because%20that%20could%20have%20just%20damaged%20the%20alliance%20and%20would%20have%20affected%20our%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Paswan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20won%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20with%20Mr%20Paswan's%20party%20achieving%20a%20100%20per%20cent%20strike%20rate%20by%20bagging%20all%20five%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20as%20chief%20minister%20has%20done%20%26quot%3Breally%20well%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20the%20way%20the%20state%20was%20run%20under%20the%20previous%20RJD%20governments.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20always%20a%20scope%20for%20improvement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurbing%20the%20crime%20rate%20can%20boost%20tourism%2C%20especially%20religious%20tourism%2C%20in%20the%20state%2C%20as%20people%20need%20to%20feel%20safe%20before%20visiting%20Bihar.%20A%20grand%20temple%20in%20Sitamarhi%20for%20Lord%20Ram's%20wife%20Sita%20and%20connecting%20the%20town%2C%20where%20the%20devout%20believe%20she%20was%20born%2C%20with%20Ayodhya%20can%20be%20a%20huge%20boost%20to%20tourism%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20rued%20the%20lack%20of%20education%20infrastructure%20in%20cities%20of%20Bihar%2C%20noting%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20students%20from%20the%20state%20enroll%20in%20Kota's%20coaching%20centres%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20owned%20by%20Biharis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20good%20number%20of%20teachers%20there%20are%20also%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20said%2C%20wondering%20why%20such%20a%20model%20cannot%20be%20replicated%20in%20Patna%2C%20Muzaffarpur%20or%20Bhagalpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20regularly%20suffers%20from%20drought%20and%20floods%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Hajipur%20MP%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20the%20inter-linking%20of%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721473980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6lp4c8ng_chirag-paswan_625x300_30_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-biharis-are-doing-so-well-why-is-bihar-behind-asks-union-minister-chirag-paswan-6147764%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20and%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20leader%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20asked%20the%20Bihar%20government%20to%20set%2