0have%20the%20simple%20right%20to%20practice%20their%20faith%20and%20beliefs%20of%20non-violence%20in%20their%20own%20holy%20town%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20editorial%2C%20titled%20'Meat%20ban%20disregards%20majority%20food%20culture'%2C%20Deccan%20Herald%20commented%20on%20the%20ban%20on%20selling%20or%20consuming%20non-vegetarian%20food%20in%20Palitana%2C%20a%20prominent%20Jain%20pilgrimage%20site%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20imposed%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20places%20like%20Kurukshetra%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Haridwar%20in%20Uttarakhand%20have%20also%20placed%20restrictions%20on%20non-vegetarian%20restaurants%20and%20the%20open%20sale%20of%20meat%2C%20fish%20and%20eggs%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20bans%20disproportionately%20impact%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20which%20supplies%20meat%20and%20poultry%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20population%2C%20which%20consumes%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Jains%20abstain%20from%20onions%2C%20potatoes%2C%20and%20all%20root%20vegetables%2C%20while%20Muslims%20do%20not%20eat%20pork...%20Food%20is%20inherently%20a%20personal%20choice%2C%20and%20imposing%20one's%20dietary%20preferences%20on%20others%20is%20fundamentally%20unfair.%20Everyone%20should%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20their%20food.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20political%20high-handedness%20disregards%20the%20dietary%20practices%20of%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%2C%20including%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20scheduled%20castes%2C%20scheduled%20tribes%2C%20and%20OBCs%2C%20who%2C%20generally%20speaking%2C%20consume%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20Many%20upper-caste%20communities%20like%20Bhumihars%20and%20Rajputs%20include%20non-vegetarian%20items%20in%20their%20daily%20diet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20editorial%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20newspaper%20of%20explicitly%20targeting%20Jain%20culture%20and%20one%2