r%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorkel%20has%20also%20worked%20with%20Gambhir%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20team.%20Morkel%20played%20for%20the%20franchise%20between%202014%20and%202016%20under%20Gambhir's%20captaincy%20and%20even%20won%20the%20title%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Csection%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20stated%20that%20Dilip%20and%20Nayar%20will%20travel%20with%20the%20team%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20but%20it%20remains%20unclear%20when%20Ten%20Doeschate%20will%20join%20the%20side.%20He%20is%20currently%20working%20as%20part%20of%20the%20coaching%20staff%20for%20the%20LA%20Knight%20Riders%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Major%20League%20Cricket%20(MLC).%20The%20Board%20is%20currently%20in%20conversation%20with%20Morkel%20about%20the%20bowling%20coach%20job%20but%20nothing%20concrete%20has%20come%20out%20of%20the%20discussions%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fsection%3E%5Cn%3Csection%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20India%20squads%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%20tour%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ET20I%20Squad%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Suryakumar%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1492-suryakumar-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20(C)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20(VC)%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rinku%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106742-rinku-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERinku%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Riyan%20Parag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108566-riyan-parag-playerprofile%5C%22%