mar%2C%20Lt%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20health%2C%20based%20on%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Superintendent%20of%20the%20prison.%20Mr%20Saxena%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20may%20be%20deliberately%20avoiding%20the%20prescribed%20medical%20diet%20and%20medications%2C%20including%20insulin%2C%20despite%20having%20Type%20II%20Diabetes%20Mellitus.%20The%20letter%20alleged%20several%20instances%20of%20%26quot%3Bwillful%20low-calorie%20intake%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20despite%20being%20provided%20with%20sufficient%20home-cooked%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LG's%20office%20cited%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20medical%20reports%2C%20indicating%20variations%20between%20glucometer%20test%20readings%20and%20continuous%20glucose%20monitoring%20system%20(CGMS)%20reading.%20The%20letter%20also%20mentioned%20a%20weight%20loss%20of%202%20kg%20since%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20surrender%20on%20June%202%20attributing%20it%20to%20insufficient%20calorie%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20also%20suggests%20loss%20of%20weight%20(now%2061.5%20kg%20which%20earlier%20was%2063.5%20Kg%20on%20the%20date%20of%20surrender%20-%20June%202%2C%202024).%20Prima%20facie%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20due%20to%20less%20calorie%20intake%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20categorically%20denied%20the%20LG's%20allegations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20sugar%20level%20has%20come%20below%2050%20more%20than%208%20times.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal%20can%20go%20into%20a%20coma%2C%20and%20there%20is%20also%20a%20risk%20of%20brain%20stroke%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20Sanjay%20Singh%20also%20criticised%20the%20LG's%20letter.%20In%20a%20fiery%20post%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20kind%20of%20joke%20are%20you%20making%2C%20LG%20Sir%3F%20Would%20a%20man%20reduce%20his%20sugar%20levels%20at%20night%3F%20This%20is%20very%20dangerous.%20LG%20Sir%2C%20if%20you%20do%20not%20know%20about%20the%20disease%2C%20then%20you%20should%20not%20write%20such%20a%20letter.%20God%20forbid%20such%20a%20time%20ever%20comes%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BC%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AC%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%88%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BE%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A5%A4%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AC%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%90%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%E0%A5%A4%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A4%88%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%AD%E0%A