nts-chhole-bhature-pancakes-kachori%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(minced%20meat%20cooked%20on%20skewers)%2C%20grills%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshawarma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Middle%20Eastern%20dish%20consisting%20of%20meat%20that%20is%20cut%20into%20thin%20slices%2C%20stacked%20in%20an%20inverted%20cone%2C%20and%20roasted%20on%20a%20slow-turning%20vertical%20spit)%2C%20%3Cem%3Egol%20gappas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(deep-fried%20breaded%20hollow%20spherical%20shell%20filled%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20finely%20diced%20potato%2C%20onion%2C%20peas%2C%20and%20chickpea)%20and%20%3Cem%3Etandoori%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20(a%20dish%20made%20from%20chicken%20marinated%20in%20yoghurt%20and%20spices%20and%20roasted%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Etandoor%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20cylindrical%20clay%20oven)%20make%20up%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20area%E2%80%99s%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrilliant%20and%20unique%20though%20each%20menu%20is%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fact%20that%20owes%20to%20their%20owners%E2%80%99%20cultural%20roots%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20South%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20the%20restaurants%20at%20Curry%20Mile%20are%20bound%20by%20a%20single%20promise%3A%20to%20serve%20you%20the%20best%20%3Cem%3Echicken%20tikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%2C%20have%20a%20seat%20while%20we%20regale%20you%20with%20the%20vibrant%20(and%20debatable)%20origins%20of%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326173%2Forigins-of-iconic-indian-dishes-loved-across-the-world-food-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistory%E2%80%99s%20most%20loved%20dishes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20640px)%20100vw%2C%20640px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F36869943_2009599892410608_4959226096185769984_n-1721034983.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C