Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%20marks%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354285%2Fias-officer-taruni-pandey-upsc-cse-timetable-strategy-mains-prelims-tips-tricks-jamtara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuccess%20in%20competitive%20exams%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20ultimate%20measure%20of%20achievement%2C%20the%20pressure%20can%20be%20immense.%20Thankfully%2C%20things%20are%20changing%20and%20there%20are%20a%20few%20harbingers%20of%20hope%20on%20the%20horizon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJigyasu%20Agarwal%20had%20tears%20in%20his%20eyes%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20results%20of%20the%20UPSC%20Mains%20in%202022.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20his%20name%20on%20the%20shortlist.%20Several%20kilometres%20away%2C%20in%20another%20city%2C%20Gargi%20Gupta%20too%20faced%20the%20same%20dejection.%20She%20missed%20out%20on%20clearing%20the%20UPSC%20Prelims%20by%20a%20few%20marks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20country%2C%20every%20UPSC%20result%20leaves%20several%20aspirants%20heartbroken.%20While%20some%20decide%20to%20give%20it%20another%20shot%2C%20others%20try%20to%20find%20different%20paths.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20most%20aspirants%20seldom%20have%20a%20Plan%20B%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJigyasu%2C%2027%2C%20a%20committed%20rationalist%2C%20had%20already%20decided%20that%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20more%20than%20three%20attempts.%20After%20deciding%20to%20look%20beyond%20UPSC%2C%20he%20waged%20a%20lone%20battle%20to%20find%20a%20good%20job%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20cousin%2C%20Akshat%20Agarwal%2C%20also%20walked%20a%20similar%20path%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20Both%20brothers%2C%20who%20underwent%20tumultuous%20journeys%20before%20finding%20their%20niches%20in%20the%20professional%20world%2C%20established%20a%20venture%20named%20Rebounce.%20Born%20out%20of%20a%20vision%20to%20help%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants%20transition%20smoothly%20into%20successful%20careers%2C%20Rebounce%20offers%20a%20second%20chance%20for%20aspirants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20second%20chance%20for%20aspirants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20village%20in%20Bishnoi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Jigyasu%20pursued%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353376%2Fabhijeet-gan-rite-water-solutions-million-litres-clean-drinking-water-jal-jeevan-mission-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectrical%20engineering%20from%20NIT%20%3C%2Fa%3E(National%20Institute%20of%20Technology)%20Patna.%20He%20was%20placed%20in%20ABB%20Ltd%2C%20a%20Swedish%E2%80%93Swiss%20multinational%20corporation.%20Despite%20having%20a%20good%20job%2C%20he%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98purposelessness%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWNhLIgqvyiw%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Skill%20sets%20of%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20for%20purpose%20led%20him%20to%20pursue%20civil%20services%2C%20quitting%20his%20job%20in%20the%20process.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20an%20impact%20through%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jigyasu%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202019%20to%202021%2C%20he%20prepared%20for%20the%20UPSC%20with%20his%20whole%20heart%20and%20soul.%20In%20the%20first%20attempt%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20the%20Prelims%2C%20while%20he%20was%20able%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20Mains%20in%20the%20next%20one.%20He%20then%20chose%20to%20join%20his%20family%20business%2C%20a%20books%20and%20stationery%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20a%20third%20attempt%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287625%2Fwhat-to-do-if-you-fail-upsc-cse-exam-naman-srivastava-viral-twitter-thread%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecided%20to%20look%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Why%20he%20decided%20to%20do%20this%20is%20a%20lesson%20in%20pragmatism.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20three%20attempts%2C%20the%20sunk%20cost%20fallacy%20kicks%20in%2C%20and%20you%20always%20feel%20that%20you%20are%20very%20close%20to%20clearing%20the%20exam.%20You%20keep%20wanting%20to%20give%20it%20one%20more%20attempt.%20This%20process%20can%20consume%20your%20twenties%2C%20making%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20transition%20to%20something%20else%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Jigyasu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%20that%20the%20selection%20rate%20in%20civil%20services%20is%20about%200.1%20percent%2C%20so%20even%20the%20best%20candidates%20have%20a%20high%20probability%20of%20not%20making%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThinking%20in%20your%20early%20twenties%20that%20you%20will%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20become%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20years%20it%20takes%2C%20might%20sound%20courageous.%20But%20if%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20out%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ve%20spent%20six%20to%20seven%20years%20preparing%20for%20UPSC%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20hard%20to%20do%20something%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20to%20transitioning%20to%20a%20different%20career%20was%20not%20a%20smooth%20one%20for%20either%20Jigyasu%20or%20Akshat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshat%20had%20harboured%20a%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20civil%20servant%20since%20Class%209.%20He%20completed%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20economics%2C%20worked%20for%20a%20year%20and%20resigned%20to%20focus%20on%20UPSC%20exams.%20After%20two%20unsuccessful%20attempts%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20a%20corporate%20career.%20Both%20brothers%20recall%20reaching%20out%20to%20friends%2C%20college%20mates%2C%20former%20colleagues%20and%20ex-UPSC%20aspirants.%20To%20their%20dismay%2C%20none%20of%20them%20really%20helped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20reached%20out%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20and%20applied%20to%20hundreds%20of%20organisations.%20Very%20few%20were%20kind%20enough%20to%20respond.%20What%20I%20struggled%20with%20was%20finding%20my%20niche.%20Deciding%20an%20alternate%20career%20was%20difficult%20as%20I%20was%20an%20engineer%20by%20education%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20business%20strategy%20and%20later%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20policy%20and%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jigyasu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20narrowing%20down%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20political%20consulting%20as%20areas%20of%20interest%2C%20he%20spent%20about%20six%20months%20upskilling%20himself%20through%20online%20courses%20like%20Coursera%20and%20YouTube%20videos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20job%20in%20a%20political%20consultancy%20firm.%20When%20the%20two%20brothers%20met%20after%20this%2C%20the%20conversation%20turned%20heavy%20when%20they%20shared%20experiences%20about%20the%20difficult%20road%20they%20embarked%20on%20to%20reach%20here.%20A%20lack%20of%20guidance%20and%20mentorship%20jarringly%20stood%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20smooth%20transition%20to%20a%20corporate%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20impact%2C%20the%20duo%20launched%20Rebounce%20in%20October%202023.%20The%20social%20enterprise%20aims%20to%20render%20robust%20support%20to%20fellow%20aspirants%20transitioning%20from%20UPSC%20preparations%20to%20alternative%20fulfilling%20careers.%20Its%20mission%20is%20crafted%20around%20offering%20these%20individuals%20a%20%E2%80%98second%20chance%E2%80%99%20by%20opening%20doors%20to%20numerous%20opportunities%20and%20guiding%20them%20towards%20satisfying%20career%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7218026798205321216%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221256%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGargi%20(25)%20worked%20towards%20UPSC%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20after%20completing%20her%20undergraduate%20degree.%20When%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20the%20exam%20after%20three%20attempts%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20look%20at%20greener%20pastures.%20But%20what%20they%20would%20be%20remained%20a%20question%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20unsure%20about%20her%20next%20steps%2C%20she%20heard%20about%20Rebounce.%20She%20reached%20out%20and%20received%20a%20mentorship%20session%20from%20Akshat%20and%20Jigyasu.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20confused%20about%20what%20path%20to%20take%20next.%20While%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20the%20development%20sector%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20get%20in%2C%20which%20NGOs%20to%20apply%20to%2C%20which%20fellowships%20I%20should%20aim%20for.%20I%20had%20nobody%20to%20guide%20me.%20Rebounce%20helped%20me%20by%20charting%20a%20path%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJigyasu%20explains%20that%20when%20an%20ex-UPSC%20aspirant%20approaches%20them%2C%20they%20first%20conduct%20a%20free%20mentorship%20session%20to%20help%20them%20envision%20a%20path.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20question%20in%20most%20of%20their%20minds%20is%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERebounce%20helps%20them%20by%20understanding%20their%20interests%2C%20aspirations%20and%20skills.%20Based%20on%20these%2C%20they%20give%20them%20certain%20options%20for%20possible%20careers.%20Their%20flagship%20market%20readiness%20programme%20offers%20support%20at%20five%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESupport%20provided%20by%20Rebounce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20to%20do%20next%3A%20Decided%20based%20on%20skills%2C%20aspirations%2C%20and%20interests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne-on-one%20guidance%3A%20Co-founders%20guide%20candidates%20with%20whatever%20doubts%20they%20have.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUpskilling%3A%20Courses%20and%20upskilling%20programmes%20to%20bridge%20skill%20gaps.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPortfolio%20building%3A%20Projects%2C%20fellowships%2C%20and%20volunteering%20to%20gain%20hands-on%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBuilding%20a%20Resume%2FLinkedIn%20Profile%3A%20Creating%20an%20industry-recognised%20resume%20and%20compelling%20cover%20letter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInterview%20readiness%3A%20Preparing%20candidates%20to%20convert%20their%20skills%20into%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECorporate%20referrals%3A%20Connecting%20candidates%20through%20a%20professional%20network.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Rebounce%20has%20helped%20over%20300%20former%20UPSC%20aspirants%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20now%20working%20in%20public%20policy%2C%20impact%20consulting%2C%20NGOs%20and%20other%20corporates%2C%20shares%20Jigyasu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enterprise%20mainly%20helps%20ex-aspirants%20showcase%20the%20skills%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20table.%20Jigyasu%20opines%20that%20the%20market%20does%20not%20recognise%20the%20unique%20skills%20that%20an%20ex-UPSC%20aspirant%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20a%20blank%20gap%20of%20four%20to%20five%20years%2C%20recruiters%20should%20look%20at%20the%20skills%20that%20preparing%20for%20this%20exam%20builds%20in%20you.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311132%2Fmother-daughter-sustainable-lifestyle-brand-helps-homemakers-earn-bags-shark-tank-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecandidates%20have%20