oopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F306168%2Findian-oil-indoor-solar-cooking-stove-surya-nutan-save-lpg-reduce-carbon-footprint%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20energy%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20is%20abundantly%20available%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20people%20think%20solar%20cooking%20is%20not%20convenient.%20With%20our%20experience%20of%20completely%20switching%20to%20solar%20cooking%2C%20we%20find%20it%20more%20convenient%20and%20easier%20than%20an%20LPG%20stove.%20Secondly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20guilt-free%20cooking.%20There%20is%20an%20immense%20satisfaction%20knowing%20our%20food%20is%20cooked%20in%20sunlight%20effortlessly.%20We%20are%20not%20exploiting%20our%20planet%E2%80%99s%20resources%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Reva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20managed%20to%20close%20this%20energy%20loop%20for%20ourselves.%20If%20this%20becomes%20aspirational%20and%20households%20use%20sunlight%20as%20energy%20then%20collectively%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20mitigate%20the%20climate%20crisis.%20All%20of%20us%20can%20think%20of%20adopting%20solar%20cooking%20as%20our%20first%20step%20towards%20energy%20self-sufficiency%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESource%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fenergy%2Foil-gas%2Flpg-imports-surge-60-in-five-years%2Farticleshow%2F107732630.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELPG%20imports%20surge%2060%25%20in%20five%20years%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20Sanjeev%20Choudhary%20for%20Economic%20Times%2C%20published%20on%2016%20February%202024.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Reva%20Jhingan%20Malik.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721209794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%