elling%2C%20we%20wake%20up%20early%2C%20explore%20the%20place%2C%20and%20then%20start%20working%20around%2011%20am.%20We%20work%20until%20about%206pm%2C%20take%20small%20breaks%20in%20between%2C%20and%20then%20spend%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20editing%20videos%20at%20night.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20prioritising%20travel%20and%20making%20the%20most%20of%20our%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20travelled%20to%20most%20states%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20initial%20goal%20was%20to%20cover%20ten%20states%20in%20a%20year.%20Recently%2C%20we%20went%20from%20Mangaluru%20to%20Srinagar.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20almost%20all%20the%20central%20states%2C%20taking%20about%20a%20month%20to%20explore%20each%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20most%20states%20except%20for%20five%20in%20the%20Northeast%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346358%2Fbest-homestays-in-western-ghats-for-a-summer-getaway-goa-panchgani-list-2024%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20the%20Western%20Ghats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Overall%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20covered%20nearly%20all%20the%20states%20on%20our%20bike%20except%20for%20a%20few%20regions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d702PPYWZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d702PPYWZ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fd