E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20cost%20accountant%20first%20came%20across%20the%20harmful%20pesticides%20being%20used%20on%20the%20crops%2C%20he%20spent%20several%20sleepless%20nights.%20To%20learn%20about%20organic%20farming%20practices%2C%20he%20took%20a%20sabbatical%20from%20his%20job%20at%20General%20Electric%20(GE)%20and%20spent%20a%20few%20months%20visiting%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20farmers%20in%20Jalgaon%20and%20other%20regions%20of%20Maharashtra%20practise%20organic%20farming%20made%20the%20cost%20accountant%20understand%20that%20farming%20can%20be%20done%20the%20way%20nature%20intended%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20green%20revolution%2C%20farmers%20in%20India%20were%20essentially%20practising%20organic%20farming.%20All%20we%20had%20to%20do%20was%20go%20back%20several%20decades%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20sounds%20great%20on%20paper%2C%20once%20the%20soil%20gets%20used%20to%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20patience%20to%20revive%20it%20or%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFundamentally%2C%20soil%20or%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20anything%20non-natural.%20Chemicals%20are%20alien%2C%20but%20once%20you%E2%80%99ve%20pumped%20them%20in%20for%20decades%2C%20they%20get%20used%20to%20it.%20So%20we%20started%20with%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20land.%20The%20first%20and%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20the%20soil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20using%20cow%20dung%20and%20vermicompost.%20While%20in%20chemical%20farming%20on