pires%20to%20encourage%20more%20people%20to%20adopt%20hydroponics.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20%3Cstrong%3EPassive%20Income%20Model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20For%20clients%20who%20intend%20to%20start%20a%20large-scale%20hydroponics%20business%20but%20lack%20the%20bandwidth%20to%20manage%20the%20farms%2C%20Farmcult%20offers%20comprehensive%20support.%20They%20not%20only%20help%20set%20up%20the%20farm%20but%20also%20manage%20daily%20operations%2C%20right%20from%20germination%20to%20harvesting%20and%20market%20linkages.%20Farmcult%20shares%20quarterly%20returns%20with%20clients%20who%20have%20invested%20in%20the%20farm.%20Pritpal%20says%20that%20they%20are%20currently%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20people%20for%20this%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmcult%20also%20provides%20workshops%20and%20training%20to%20the%20community%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20hydroponic%20farming%2C%20including%20sustainability%2C%20water%20efficiency%2C%20and%20chemical-free%20produce.%20They%20have%20trained%20more%20than%20100%20people%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdit%20Bhatia%2C%20who%20trained%20under%20Pritpal%20last%20April%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnyone%20can%20practise%20hydroponics%20farming.%20It%20is%20very%20useful%20for%20crops%20like%20lettuce%2C%20where%20the%20growth%20cycle%20reduces%20from%2090%20to%2040%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFormal%20training%20becomes%20essential%20in%20hydroponics%20to%20get%20maximum%20yield%20and%20return%20on%20investment.%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20maintain%20water%20temperature%20and%20control%20humidity%20levels.%20It%20is%20also%20essential%20to%20check%20for%20fungus%20attacks%20as%20they%20can%20quickly%20spread%20throughout%20the%20farm%20due%20to%20the%20shared%20water%20source.%20Using%20chillers%20can%20reduce%20temperatures%20to%2020%20degrees%20and%20minimise%20fungal%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20a